Check FAQ for how to install: http://www.open-mpi.de/faq/?category=building

If installing on a cluster FAQ26 is useful

26. How do I build Open MPI with support for [my favorite network type]?

SLURM is automatically supported, LSF has to be configured, see
31. How do I build Open MPI with support for Platform LSF?

Building with CUDA aware support
34. How do I build Open MPI with CUDA-aware support?

Use `--enable-mpi-thread-multiple`
